Package: open-agenda
Architecture: all
Version: 1.4.0
Maintainer: Open-Agenda Team <team@open-agenda.org>
Depends: python3, python3-tk
Description: OpenAgenda v1.4 - Ultimate 2025 Experience
 The ultimate agenda - Now with auto-update, weather, and enhanced UI!
 .
 Features:
  - Auto-update from GitHub
  - Weather via OpenWeather API
  - Glassmorphism & frosted glass effects
  - Vibrant gradient backgrounds
  - Neon glow effects
  - Modern floating elements
  - Dark mode with neon accents
  - Dashboard stats
  - Auto-save with local storage
  - Search
